Vicki Momberg is nowhere to be found. She failed to hand herself over to police in August, after her appeal against a crimen injuria conviction failed. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The racist's on the run. Vicki Momberg is nowhere to be found. She failed to hand herself over to police in August after her appeal against a crimen injuria conviction failed. READ: Convicted racist Vicki Momberg in hiding Momberg was found guilty of repeatedly calling a black police officer the k-word and was handed a two-year sentence. It seems the long arm of the law is having a hard time locating Momberg. Where could she possibly be? eNCA reporter, Nqobile Madlala hit the streets of Joburg in search of her.